   Van Nest, Byron N.; Worley, Anne C., Univ Manitoba, Dept Biol Sci, 212B Biol Sci Bldg, Winnipeg, MB R3T 2N2, Canada.
   Edge, Andrea A., Northside High Sch, Lafayette, LA USA.},
