Abstract = {Kigelia pinnata speculated to show late acting self incompatibility was
   subjected to critical observational analysis of its floral biology and
   it was found that the mechanism of anther opening varies within the
   anthers of a single flower and between the flowers of the same tree. The
   present study indicates that the mechanism of pollen presentation is
